<span id="freeTextContainer4391830970640491844">This one of those books I loved for the hero, and wanted to drop the heroine off a cliff. Back in the day, that was rare. Usually the heroes were jerks with a capital J, and I just wanted the heroine to get away from the hero and give a rude gesture as she walks away. I should reread this. It&apos;s a long book, though. Probably should finally read Outlander, first.</span>
