<div id="review_1377428931" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1377428931" />
    <a title="Sheila Majczan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/29962439-sheila-majczan"><img alt="Sheila Majczan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1422396088p2/29962439.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1377428931?book_show_action=true">Aug 29, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sheila Majczan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sheila Majczan" href="/user/show/29962439-sheila-majczan">Sheila Majczan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1377428931" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16745191815329323900">I read this and all of Kathleen&apos;s books many years ago. She is my favorite historical romance author. Yes, there is sex but the relationships are always monogamous.<br/><br/>Shana thinks she is smart as she marries a condemned felon, Ruark, (Don&apos;t you love that name?) to meet her father&apos;s deadline for a marriage or he will force her to marry his choice. She even sends her servant to witness his hanging to make sure she is a &quot;widow&quot;. But as she and her father sail for home, from England to the Caribbean, s</span>
  <span id="freeText16745191815329323900" style="display:none">I read this and all of Kathleen's books many years ago. She is my favorite historical romance author. Yes, there is sex but the relationships are always monogamous.<br /><br />Shana thinks she is smart as she marries a condemned felon, Ruark, (Don't you love that name?) to meet her father's deadline for a marriage or he will force her to marry his choice. She even sends her servant to witness his hanging to make sure she is a "widow". But as she and her father sail for home, from England to the Caribbean, she espies among the slaves and indentured servants being led on board in chains...Guess who?<br /><br />As she learns during her many encounters with this man "the mind cannot tell the heart with whom to fall in love and some times it selects the worst of choices". Set in England, on an island and then in the Colonies we follow Shanna through many adventures and trysts in a tale you won't be able to put down.<br /><br />Spoiled golden girl meets handsome condemned poor boy. Way up on the top of my favorites pile.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16745191815329323900" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


